Applications:

 ctaskbrowser [IOR|ControlTaskName]
   A TaskBrowser which connects to a remote TaskContext using CORBA,
   and allows the user to manipulate the remote tasks as if they were local.

 cdeployer [ControlTaskName]
   A DeploymentComponent which runs as a CORBA server, waiting for
   requests. Connect to this application using the ctaskbrowser.

 deployer 
   A DeploymentComponent which runs locally and starts up a TaskBrowser
   console, waiting for user commands. No CORBA required or used.